snippet.title: The Sims 2 Mobile (2005, Java) | gameplay, no commentary
snippet.description:
Gameplay of The Sims 2 Mobile (unconnected edition for low-end phones). The Sims 2 was released in 2005 for mobile phones capable of running Java applications such as Nokia 6600. This version is for less powerful phones and this video mainly serves as a comparison to the high-end version, gameplay of which you can find here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IeFkaQNSZRA.
You can read more about the game here https://sims.fandom.com/wiki/The_Sims_2_(mobile)

Please be aware that the game features no music and only a handful of sound effects that might be too loud unless you adjust your volume beforehand.
